                "Description": "<section itemscope itemtype=\"https://schema.org/Organization\">\n  <h2 itemprop=\"name\">Finance Division</h2>\n  <p itemprop=\"description\">The EFG Finance division serves as the central hub for financial operations and strategy within the ESL FACEIT Group. Its primary purpose is to streamline internal workflows, ensure consistency across the department, and provide transparency into financial operations. The division acts as the single source of truth for all financial policies, standard operating procedures (SOPs), and strategic documentation, supporting the professional growth of team members and facilitating cross-departmental collaboration.</p>\n  <h3>Core Pillars</h3>\n  <ul>\n    <li><strong>Accounting:</strong> Manages period-end closing schedules, the chart of accounts, and financial reporting standards.</li>\n    <li><strong>Treasury:</strong> Oversees cash management protocols, banking authorizations, and FX hedging policies.</li>\n    <li><strong>Tax &amp; Transfer Pricing:</strong> Handles compliance calendars, intercompany agreements, and jurisdictional tax guides.</li>\n    <li><strong>Controlling, FP&amp;A:</strong> Responsible for budgeting templates, forecasting cycles, and variance analysis frameworks.</li>\n    <li><strong>Procurement:</strong> Manages vendor onboarding processes, PO approval workflows, and preferred supplier lists.</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>",
